trans-unit.source: Phase 2 - Initial Preparation/Analysis and Merging
trans-unit.target: Phase 2 - Initial Preparation/Analysis and Merging

trans-unit.source: Allows to prepare/analyze a new project and merge back the translated files.
trans-unit.target: Allows to prepare/analyze a new project and merge back the translated files.

trans-unit.source: This phase only substitute XTM to the Trados process.
trans-unit.target: This phase only substitute XTM to the Trados process.

trans-unit.source: The extraction to XLIFF and merging back is done by XTM.
trans-unit.target: The extraction to XLIFF and merging back is done by XTM.

trans-unit.source: The t-kits generated by XTM are treated like XLIFF files generated by Trados-Studio.
trans-unit.target: The t-kits generated by XTM are treated like XLIFF files generated by Trados-Studio.

trans-unit.source: The MT pre-translation of the files is done through the MT portal like with Trados files.
trans-unit.target: The MT pre-translation of the files is done through the MT portal like with Trados files.

trans-unit.source: The TMs are managed in XTM.
trans-unit.target: The TMs are managed in XTM.

trans-unit.source: The analysis is done by XTM.
trans-unit.target: The analysis is done by XTM.

trans-unit.source: If needed, un-supported files can be done by a manual pre/post-process.
trans-unit.target: If needed, un-supported files can be done by a manual pre/post-process.

trans-unit.source: Phase 3 - Pre/Post-Processing Options
trans-unit.target: Phase 3 - Pre/Post-Processing Options

trans-unit.source: Allows a more automated pre/post-processing of the files XTM cannot handle directly.
trans-unit.target: Allows a more automated pre/post-processing of the files XTM cannot handle directly.

trans-unit.source: Some file formats may not be handled as necessary by XTM.
trans-unit.target: Some file formats may not be handled as necessary by XTM.

trans-unit.source: In that case, the user can select the filter configuration to apply to the file before it get sent to XTM.
trans-unit.target: In that case, the user can select the filter configuration to apply to the file before it get sent to XTM.

trans-unit.source: The files with such configurations are extracted to XLIFF and the XLIFF files is used as input for XTM.
trans-unit.target: The files with such configurations are extracted to XLIFF and the XLIFF files is used as input for XTM.

trans-unit.source: When merging back, the post-processing merges back the translated XLIFF back into its original format.
trans-unit.target: When merging back, the post-processing merges back the translated XLIFF back into its original format.
